== Installation ==
'''11.''' Create folder <code>/usr/local/lib/python3.9/dist-packages/</code>.

{{CodeSelect|code=
sudo mkdir -p /usr/local/lib/python3.9/dist-packages/
}}

'''12.''' Install <code>pylru.py</code> into folder <code>/usr/local/lib/python3.9/dist-packages/</code>.

{{CodeSelect|code=
sudo cp ~/pylru/pylru.py /usr/local/lib/python3.9/dist-packages/
}}

'''13.''' Done.

Installation of PyLRU has been completed.

